Package com.quinsoft.zeidon.android

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ZeidonDisplayView
    A Zeidon android views that displays data is an output view and must implement this interface.
    ZeidonInputView
    Views that implement this interface are used to set Zeidon attribute values.
    ZeidonTaskQualifier
    An android view that implements this interface can supply a Zeidon TaskQualification object (either a task or view) that is used for retrieving Zeidon views by name.

    ZeidonAndroidViewDelegate

    ZeidonEditText
    EditText view for editing Zeidon attribute values.
    ZeidonEntitySpinner
    Creates an Android Spinner that is populated by the twins of a Zeidon entity.
